data.description: If you are looking for the perfect move-in ready home, then look no further! This beautiful 2007 Lehigh Acres home is 4/2 with vaulted ceilings & screened lanai. You don’t want to miss this spacious, well-maintained home, sitting on a ¼ acre lot with nearly 1700 sq. ft. under air. This open-concept, split-bedroom floor plan provides ample space for a growing family, with plenty of natural light great for entertaining. Large master bedroom with his/her walk-in closets, and ensuite bathroom with dual sinks. The 2nd bathroom was completely redone and has a convenient access door to the lanai. The 2-car garage provides secure parking, and the large driveway provides ample parking for guests. The manicured lawn, freshly landscaped plants, mature trees, and wood privacy fence allow you to enjoy your beautiful backyard in seclusion.  A 4-zone irrigation system keeps the lawn and plants healthy and green. The interior and exterior of the home were refreshed with new floors and paint in August 2023. Conveniently located, this property provides easy access to State Rd 82, Daniels Pkwy, Gunnery Rd, Lee Blvd, Sunshine Blvd, I-75, the RSW Airport, and much more.
